Date: 1993-12-14

Title: Deformation Quantization of the Isotropic Rotator

Authors: A. Stern and I. Yakushin

Comments: 12pp, LATEX

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A10 (1995) 399-408

We perform a deformation quantization of the classical isotropic rigidrotator. The resulting quantum system is not invariant under the usual$SU(2)\times SU(2)$ chiral symmetry, but instead $SU_{q^{-1}}(2) \timesSU_q(2)$.